The paper discusses the use of Behavior Driven Development (BDD) in the context of Enterprise Information Systems (EIS), which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of Business Process Modeling (BPM), which is related to database systems (cs.DB) and programming languages (cs.PL). The proposal of using Finite State Machines (FSM) is also related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
